text.value:
Main samajh gaya aapki requirement. Aap WhatsApp messages ko bulk select karna chahte hain AccessibilityService use karke. Main aapko complete implementation guide de raha hun:

## AccessibilityService mein WhatsApp Message Selection Feature

### 1. AccessibilityService Class mein ye methods add karein:

```java
public class MyAccessibilityService extends AccessibilityService {

    private boolean isSelectionMode = false;
    private AccessibilityNodeInfo firstSelectedMessage = null;

    @Override
    public void onAccessibilityEvent(AccessibilityEvent event) {
        if (event.getPackageName() != null &amp;&amp; 
            event.getPackageName().toString().equals(&quot;com.whatsapp&quot;)) {

            // Check if selection mode is active
            if (isSelectionMode) {
                performMessageSelection();
            }
        }
    }

    // Method to start selection mode
    public void startBulkSelection() {
        isSelectionMode = true;
        // Find currently selected message
        AccessibilityNodeInfo rootNode = getRootInActiveWindow();
        if (rootNode != null) {
            firstSelectedMessage = findSelectedMessage(rootNode);
            if (firstSelectedMessage != null) {
                selectAllMessagesBelow();
            }
        }
    }

    // Find already selected message
    private AccessibilityNodeInfo findSelectedMessage(AccessibilityNodeInfo node) {
        if (node == null) return null;

        // Check if current node is selected
        if (node.isSelected() || node.isChecked()) {
            return node;
        }

        // Recursively check children
        for (int i = 0; i &lt; node.getChildCount(); i++) {
            AccessibilityNodeInfo child = node.getChild(i);
            AccessibilityNodeInfo result = findSelectedMessage(child);
            if (result != null) return result;
        }
        return null;
    }

    // Select all messages below the first selected one
    private void selectAllMessagesBelow() {
        AccessibilityNodeInfo rootNode = getRootInActiveWindow();
        if (rootNode == null) return;

        // Find RecyclerView containing messages
        AccessibilityNodeInfo recyclerView = findNodeByClassName(rootNode, 
            &quot;androidx.recyclerview.widget.RecyclerView&quot;);

        if (recyclerView != null) {
            boolean foundFirst = false;

            // Iterate through all messages
            for (int i = 0; i &lt; recyclerView.getChildCount(); i++) {
                AccessibilityNodeInfo messageNode = recyclerView.getChild(i);

                if (messageNode != null) {
                    // Check if we've found our first selected message
                    if (!foundFirst &amp;&amp; isNodeSelected(messageNode)) {
                        foundFirst = true;
                        continue;
                    }

                    // Select all messages after the first one
                    if (foundFirst) {
                        performLongClick(messageNode);
                    }
                }
            }
        }
    }

    // Helper method to check if node is selected
    private boolean isNodeSelected(AccessibilityNodeInfo node) {
        if (node == null) return false;

        // Check node and its children for selection state
        if (node.isSelected() || node.isChecked()) {
            return true;
        }

        for (int i = 0; i &lt; node.getChildCount(); i++) {
            if (isNodeSelected(node.getChild(i))) {
                return true;
            }
        }
        return false;
    }

    // Perform long click on message to select
    private void performLongClick(AccessibilityNodeInfo node) {
        if (node != null &amp;&amp; node.isLongClickable()) {
            node.performAction(AccessibilityNodeInfo.ACTION_LONG_CLICK);
        }
    }

    // Find node by class name
    private AccessibilityNodeInfo findNodeByClassName(AccessibilityNodeInfo node, 
                                                     String className) {
        if (node == null) return null;

        if (className.equals(node.getClassName())) {
            return node;
        }

        for (int i = 0; i &lt; node.getChildCount(); i++) {
            AccessibilityNodeInfo result = findNodeByClassName(node.getChild(i), className);
            if (result != null) return result;
        }
        return null;
    }

    @Override
    public void onInterrupt() {
        isSelectionMode = false;
    }
}
```

### 2. Activity mein Button Setup:

```java
public class MainActivity extends AppCompatActivity {

    private Button selectAllButton;
    private MyAccessibilityService accessibilityService;

    @Override
    protected void onCreate(Bundle savedInstanceState) {
        super.onCreate(savedInstanceState);
        setContentView(R.layout.activity_main);

        selectAllButton = findViewById(R.id.selectAllButton);

        selectAllButton.setOnClickListener(new View.OnClickListener() {
            @Override
            public void onClick(View v) {
                // Check if accessibility service is enabled
                if (isAccessibilityServiceEnabled()) {
                    // Send broadcast to trigger selection
                    Intent intent = new Intent(&quot;com.yourapp.SELECT_ALL_MESSAGES&quot;);
                    sendBroadcast(intent);

                    // Show instruction
                    Toast.makeText(MainActivity.this, 
                        &quot;WhatsApp mein ek message select karke rakho, phir yahan click karo&quot;, 
                        Toast.LENGTH_LONG).show();
                } else {
                    // Redirect to accessibility settings
                    Intent intent = new Intent(Settings.ACTION_ACCESSIBILITY_SETTINGS);
                    startActivity(intent);
                }
            }
        });
    }

    private boolean isAccessibilityServiceEnabled() {
        String service = getPackageName() + &quot;/&quot; + MyAccessibilityService.class.getCanonicalName();
        int enabled = Settings.Secure.getInt(getContentResolver(), 
            Settings.Secure.ACCESSIBILITY_ENABLED, 0);

        if (enabled == 1) {
            String settingValue = Settings.Secure.getString(getContentResolver(), 
                Settings.Secure.ENABLED_ACCESSIBILITY_SERVICES);
            return settingValue != null &amp;&amp; settingValue.contains(service);
        }
        return false;
    }
}
```

### 3. BroadcastReceiver add karein AccessibilityService mein:

```java
// AccessibilityService class mein ye add karein
private BroadcastReceiver selectionReceiver = new BroadcastReceiver() {
    @Override
    public void onReceive(Context context, Intent intent) {
        if (&quot;com.yourapp.SELECT_ALL_MESSAGES&quot;.equals(intent.getAction())) {
            startBulkSelection();
        }
    }
};

@Override
protected void onServiceConnected() {
    super.onServiceConnected();
    // Register broadcast receiver
    IntentFilter filter = new IntentFilter(&quot;com.yourapp.SELECT_ALL_MESSAGES&quot;);
    registerReceiver(selectionReceiver, filter);
}

@Override
public void onDestroy() {
    super.onDestroy();
    unregisterReceiver(selectionReceiver);
}
```

### 4. AndroidManifest.xml mein permissions:

```xml
&lt;uses-permission android:name=&quot;android.permission.BIND_ACCESSIBILITY_SERVICE&quot; /&gt;

&lt;!-- Service declaration already exists, just update if needed --&gt;
&lt;service
    android:name=&quot;.MyAccessibilityService&quot;
    android:permission=&quot;android.permission.BIND_ACCESSIBILITY_SERVICE&quot;&gt;
    &lt;intent-filter&gt;
        &lt;action android:name=&quot;android.accessibilityservice.AccessibilityService&quot; /&gt;
    &lt;/intent-filter&gt;
    &lt;meta-data
        android:name=&quot;android.accessibilityservice&quot;
        android:resource=&quot;@xml/accessibility_service_config&quot; /&gt;
&lt;/service&gt;
```

### 5. Usage Instructions:

1. App open karein
2. WhatsApp mein jao aur group open karo
3. Ek message ko long press karke select karo
4. App mein wapas aao aur &quot;Select All Below&quot; button press karo
5. WhatsApp mein wapas jao - selected message ke neeche saare messages select ho jayenge

### Important Notes:

- Ye feature WhatsApp ke UI changes ke saath break ho sakta hai
- User ko manually ek message select karna padega pehle
- AccessibilityService ko proper permissions chahiye
- Testing real device pe karna better hai

Koi specific part samajh nahi aaya ho to batayein, main aur detail mein explain kar dunga.
